  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improved Glue for Trapping Black Flies</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sightsavers, in collaboration with Federal Ministry of Health, is implementing a research project to compare six adhesives on esperanza window traps and human landing catches for black flies in Nigeria. We will aim to determine the performance of candidate glues in different ecological biotypes, and their potential for mass deployment. The outcome is expected to improve mass deployment of EWT for onchocerciasis elimination evaluations and assessments of onchocerciasis transmission dynamics.</narrative>
  </description>
